                    Ok first off i have to say this is THE best topic i have EVER read PEIROD!!!!! I am one of your biggest admierers. The reason i like you is because you are not a jerk like a lot of people on the boards you are actually a nice guy. You even inspiered me to write my own story called MYTHRAN ORIGINS which i will be posting soon. I wanted to ask if i could use something from your story.Now i know about how you feel and what you'v about the major so ill respect that and not use or ask to use him. I wanted to know if i could go more into detail about the "gift" the first builders gave to the people of crux, you see my guys name is called Mythran Stone and he finds out in my story that he has something called "imagination" in his blood and he finds this out by the voices of the great builders he hears. It would help my story a lot and i wouldnt change a thing on how the people of crux got there or any thing else thet you wrote about i just want to tie something to the "gift". i would also would reference them to your story because it would be connected with mine. Please concider this and let me know what you think.<BR /><BR />                                            Yours truly, starwars7495 aka Lightninwarrior95.<BR /><BR /><BR />~Life is a lego set, open the possibilities~
                
            
			
