it hasn't gotten through <img class="emoticon emoticon-sad" id="sad" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/sad.png" alt="Sad" title="Sad" />  <BR /><BR />But really, I can't write a bio.  I don't think bios can ever do characters justice, because it is our actions that make us who we are.  If you know what a person would do and how they'd react to any situation, only then do you know the character.  <BR /><BR />If all else fails, I do plan on making it unpleasant for him or anyone else who uses the Major.  <BR /><BR />JAMMERS OFF!!!!!
                
            
			
